data.text:
Lee Hye-ri (born June 9, 1994),[1] si fiican loogu yaqaanno magac ahaan Hyeri, waa atariisho Koonfur Kuuriya ah, heesaa, iyo shaqsiyadda telefishanka. Waxay caan ku noqotay xubinta ugu yar ee kooxda gabdhaha Girl's Day, waxaana warbaahinta Koonfur Kuuriya loogu magacaabay "Walaasha Yar ee Qaranka" sababtuna waxay tahay sumcaddeeda weyn kadib markii ay ka soo muuqatay Real Men (2014).[2][3][4]

Not to be confused with Lee Hae-ri.
